vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

term.name: House Committee on Education and Workforce

bill.summary: This resolution elects Delegate James Moylan of Guam to the Committee on Education and Workforce and provides that he shall rank immediately after Representative Michael Rulli of Ohio.
